      <h1 class="centre_me">Lord's Day Worship Structure</h1>
      <div class="header-container">
        <div class="circle-image"> <img src="https://russianicons.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/jesus4thcencommodilla.jpg"
            alt="Profile"> </div>
        <div class="header-text">
          <p><em>By Ryan Reeves</em></p>
          <p><em>In the year of our Lord 2025, on the third day of January...</em></p>
          <p><em>Knowledge Transfer Article (KTA)</em><b><em><br>
              </em></b></p>
        </div>
